stays with me.’

01:11:59.231 --> 01:12:02.261
I said: ‘It’s all right.’

01:12:02.261 --> 01:12:03.261
Eighty year-old man.

01:12:03.261 --> 01:12:05.721
I was turning sixty by that time.

01:12:05.721 --> 01:12:08.471
An eighty year-old man talking like this to
Me.

01:12:08.471 --> 01:12:12.751
I said: ‘Now what is happening to this man?’

01:12:12.751 --> 01:12:22.641
And he is the chairman of the Jungian Society,
International.

01:12:22.641 --> 01:12:24.921
See the maturity of that person.

01:12:24.921 --> 01:12:27.371
Eighty year-old.

01:12:27.371 --> 01:12:33.551
In America, such cases so much.

01:12:33.551 --> 01:12:36.481
Terrible.

01:12:36.481 --> 01:12:41.171
Extremely stupid and I don’t know, they
have no confidence in themselves.

01:12:41.171 --> 01:12:43.771
All the time they think we should not get
old.

01:12:43.771 --> 01:12:50.541
So there was, on the television they showed
the cinema actors and actresses coming for

01:12:50.541 --> 01:12:55.421
a dance of ‘shake’ and they were all about
ninety years of age.

01:12:55.421 --> 01:12:57.391
