two types of problems actually.

01:15:22.491 --> 01:15:26.261
Third type doesn’t exist, or doesn’t bother
us.

01:15:26.261 --> 01:15:30.131
One is the left another is the right, you
see.

01:15:30.131 --> 01:15:33.931
Now the lymphatic system is actually, the
combination of both.

01:15:33.931 --> 01:15:35.491
It’s a psychosomatic disease.

01:15:35.491 --> 01:15:38.581
For that you have to do just three-candle
treatment.

01:15:38.581 --> 01:15:45.631
You see it is reduced to such a simple thing
either you do three-candle treatment, or you

01:15:45.631 --> 01:15:47.301
do water treatment.

01:15:47.301 --> 01:15:57.971
The third type is the one where you have been
to wrong gurus, in the center.

01:15:57.971 --> 01:16:01.021
If I run some wrong type of meditation [INAUDIBLE].

01:16:01.021 --> 01:16:05.181
