mostly.

01:16:05.181 --> 01:16:10.761
Or maybe if the [INAUDIBLE] comes there’s
a little change also sometimes.

01:16:10.761 --> 01:16:13.711
But whatever it is, this is very simple for
physical.

01:16:13.711 --> 01:16:17.791
Anybody has lymphatic system problem has to
do left side first.

01:16:17.791 --> 01:16:18.791
So this is psychosomatic.

01:16:18.791 --> 01:16:23.821
First you must get rid of the psycho side,
so do the left side.

01:16:23.821 --> 01:16:28.631
When it is cleared out, then right side is
not difficult.

01:16:28.631 --> 01:16:35.441
If you are too right-sided, then what happens,
it’s like a pendulum, you move from right

01:16:35.441 --> 01:16:36.671
to left.

01:16:36.671 --> 01:16:39.421
Then psychosomatic troubles start.

01:16:39.421 --> 01:16:44.061
The best is first to remove the left, then
is look after the right.

01:16:44.061 --> 01:16:49.131
Sahaja Yoga is a very simple way of clearing.

01:16:49.131 --> 01:16:51.271
It works.

