give you bandhan on your chakras with a candle.

01:16:57.811 --> 01:17:09.121
Put a candle on one side of the left swadisthana
and also one before the Photograph.

01:17:09.121 --> 01:17:14.281
Because it’s all due to viruses.

01:17:14.281 --> 01:17:15.761
And the viruses are there because your attention
in the left.

01:17:15.761 --> 01:17:20.471
Once your attention goes away from there you
are rid of that.

01:17:20.471 --> 01:17:21.881
All right?

01:17:21.881 --> 01:17:24.001
It’s not complicated.

01:17:24.001 --> 01:17:27.531
Sahaja Yoga is very simple.

